{"tid":924887,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【罕見癌症】3歲半妹妹面生腫瘤 父母急籌80萬救女","createTime":"2018-12-02T12:29:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-03T00:49:34.000Z","uid":44732,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2a8ce00cc7923c72df776f8ce9ca3ead67ce0217","tid":924887,"uid":44732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T12:29:54.000Z","msg":"早前小可仁BB患上罕見「神經母腫瘤」，李嘉誠出手捐200萬元援助藥費令其生命出現曙光，但其實本港仍有無數癌童同樣急待援手。3歲半的女孩童童亦患上罕見癌症橫紋肌肉瘤，其左頸及臉的癌細胞在一個半月內極速擴大至雞蛋般大，並由於腫瘤與臉上多組神經相連，暫不能做手術切除，但單靠化療及電療的成功率存疑，兼有毁容之虞。故童童父親期望能讓愛女赴台接受香港尚未引入的最新式「質子治療」法，望能重點殺滅癌細胞，惜療費高達80萬元，龍家實無法負擔，現只望有心人能捐助部份療程費用讓童童去打一場硬仗、創一個奇蹟。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n===「蘋果日報慈善基金」關顧主任將提供協助。<br />\n「童童」暖流之友編號：C4597<br />\n<br />\n「蘋果日報慈善基金」捐款方法：<br />\n- 以PPS或信用卡作網上捐款： <a href=\"http://bit.ly/applecharity\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2Fapplecharity&d=iUjNIk4lcABczLB7tWF%2FORFQyUQXuyYblCT5RSyYNoQ%3D&h=7608effb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/applecharity</a> <br />\n- 銀行存款：<br />\n　&ndash; 匯豐銀行：580-198836-001<br />\n　&ndash; 恒生銀行：368-006565-001<br />\n　&ndash; 中國銀行：012-898-00067655<br />\n　&ndash; 東亞銀行（往來戶口）：015-514-68-01678-5<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181202/58981399\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181202%2F58981399&d=iUjNIk4lcABczLB7tWF%2FORFQyUQXuyYblCT5RSyYNoQ%3D&h=8313013e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181202%2F58981399&h=a469c01c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181202/58981399</a>"},{"pid":"8c631d11141ea682cc9aa18670262b7c93fab40e","tid":924887,"uid":23416,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T12:30:20.000Z","msg":"誠哥出手未"},{"pid":"94b7ad972a7446d9277a66c5a26984e88332e9da","tid":924887,"uid":44732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8